divs: Sighting DetailsI was at home looking outside,and i just noticed a couple stationary u.f.o. s.I almost immediately said ''U.F.O. !''.Neither moved at first the both shot out in to the sky just a little slower than break the sound barrier speed.I felt dizzy throughout the encounter and for another 5 minutes after.It shot away in to outer space.
